episodes.title: The Cult Of The Real Housewife | Docu-Series Surrounding RHOSLC Mary Cosby's Church 👀 💣
episodes.description:
Welcome back, besties! We’re back from vacation and diving headfirst into the drama with a breakdown of the three-episode docu-series airing January 1st, focused on RHOSLC Housewife Mary Cosby and her Faith Temple Church.
Ex-members and individuals close to Mary are speaking out, sharing personal stories from their time inside the church. Between the rumors, serious allegations, and emotional testimonies, fans are left asking one big question: what is REALLY happening in Mary Cosby’s world?
Let’s get into it 👀
